•  Grinsted, A., et al. (2004). Application of the cross wavelet transform and wavelet coherence. Journal of Atmospheric and Solar-Terrestrial Physics, 66(6–7), 467–478.

•  Holling, C. S. (1973). Resilience and stability of ecological systems. Annual Review of Ecology and Systematics, 4, 1–23.

